title: Push Muscles Workout (Chest, Triceps, Shoulders)
description: Basic upperbody workout. Complete 3 sets of each exercise. Superset related workouts at own discretion.

title: Calisthenics 101
description: Test your endurance, core, and strength with this high intesity calisthenic workout. Superset entire routine for 3 sets. Time yourself.

title: Pull Muscles Workout (Back, biceps)
description: This workout will focus specifically on pull ups. 3 rounds. For each round, complete 3 sets of a pullup exercise (wide grip, bicep pullup, regular)

title: Leg Day of Death
description: You already know what we're here for. Straight supersets. Squats, lunges, and more squats.

title: HIIT Cardio
description: During this HIIT (High Intensity Interval Training) workout, you will break up your run into periods of jogging/running and walking. 2 minutes on, 1 minute off, for 30 minutes.
